graph TD
  Trigger[ALERT: GRC Key Collision]
  Trigger -- Sev 1 --> L1
  Trigger -- Sev 2 --> L2

  L1[L1 SOC Analyst]
  L2[L2 SecOps Engineer]

  L1 -- "Data Issue?" --> Sys
  Sys[System Administrator]

  L2 -- "mTLS Issue?" --> IAM
  IAM[Identity Team<br/>Active Directory]

  %% Resolution Loop
  IAM -- "Certificate Re-issued" --> Resolved
  Resolved[ALERT RESOLVED]

  %% Final Escalation
  IAM -- "Root CA compromised" --> Fed
  Fed[FedRAMP Liaison<br/>Agency Head]
